      <title>新兴市场股市因中国措施不力跌至五周低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/emerging-market-stocks-hit-5-week-low-as-china-steps-fall-short</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新兴市场股票周四跌至五周以来的最低点，因为中国本周第二次放松货币政策未能缓解人们对该国经济放缓的担忧。全球对人工智能的担忧加剧了人们的悲观情绪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/emerging-market-stocks-hit-5-week-low-as-china-steps-fall-short</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 10:19:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
